review_content: Very nice packaging and fast delivery value for money.
First I Faced Some Issues.After Resolve Those Issues Now It Working Fine.

Processor is in working condition packaging is not that great.But weird thing is that clock speed mostly runs at its fullest eg 3.3ghz even in low 2 3% load which I found little disappointed coz of this behavior it may be result in higher electricity uses n I fear of CPU life span, overall its ok. Let's see how long it last.Tanks
Best Processor in this price i3 2nd Gen Best for medium spec pc

yes it is refurbished now its been 2 3 months I ve been using this. my computer has increased performance. I had a Pentium earlier now replaced with this model. I can do more multitasking and play a few games here there too :) but this is not for gaming :)

Very good processor.....I run blendr(3d software for animation) and it runs flawllessly. I have paired it with a gt 1030 and there is almost no bottleneck in most games. Far cry new dawn runs at 40-50fps.
